  "title": "A round orange UFO spotted twice near an aerodrome airstrip in Cascavel [2014]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/05/31/a-round-orange-ufo-spotted-twice-near-an-aerodrome-airstrip-in-cascavel-2014/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-4p",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>DEC 4th, 2014.</strong> At 03h00am, an aeronautical station operator at the Cascavel Aerodrome, Paraná, reported two sightings of the same round UFO of strong and intense orange color with approximately 30 cm in size, in the interval of ten minutes, traveling towards the aerodrome after making a left turn. The object moved in an East / West direction, with an approximate speed of 180km / h and 10 NM from Cascavel.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.725. &#8220;<span class=\"s1\" style=\"color:#808000;\"><span class=\"s1\"><i>Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado (ovni) em Cascavel-PR</i></span></span>&#8220;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>DEC 4th, 2014. At 03h00am, an aeronautical station operator at the Cascavel Aerodrome, Paraná, reported two sightings of the same round UFO of strong and intense orange color with approximately 30 cm in size, in the interval of ten minutes, traveling towards the aerodrome after making a left turn. The object moved in an East [&hellip;]</p>\n",
